description.en:
"Pirate X Pirate is the First Custom-Dice Turn-Based Strategy Pirate Game in Blockchain.

Recruit your crew, form your fleet, and test your prowess battling pirates and earning rewards with PXP's in-game token economy. Conquer the oceans and appropriate boundless treasures.

As the team behind the biggest board game publisher in Thailand:
 1. We are trusted among Thai Community;
 2. We promise to bring the best gameplay experience with board game elements; 
3. Easily accessible theme of the Pirate world; 
4. Attracts external revenue stream from sponsors; 
5. Attractive NFTs of Ships and Crew;
6. 3D graphics with dice battle system."

